8dAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"2358\" data-srcset=\"/now/assets/static/crystaltwin.82a2fbd.315c7c1d18d2393825e17255f2049ea4.png 480w, /now/assets/static/crystaltwin.cbab2cf.315c7c1d18d2393825e17255f2049ea4.png 1024w, /now/assets/static/crystaltwin.2665e34.315c7c1d18d2393825e17255f2049ea4.png 1920w, /now/assets/static/crystaltwin.bf28840.315c7c1d18d2393825e17255f2049ea4.png 2358w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 2358px) 100vw, 2358px\" data-src=\"/now/assets/static/crystaltwin.bf28840.315c7c1d18d2393825e17255f2049ea4.png\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/now/assets/static/crystaltwin.bf28840.315c7c1d18d2393825e17255f2049ea4.png\" width=\"2358\"></noscript></p>\n<h2 id=\"what-is-happening-today\"><a href=\"#what-is-happening-today\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>What is happening today?</h2>\n<p>The Internet started out as a dream technology, with the power to connect and empower us all. But now, our online world is full of fake news, identity thieves, bots, bugs, viruses and big â€œbosses.\" No matter which way we look at it, the world wide web has gotten out of control.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>We log on to countless different applications with countless different logins, but our data is scattered and owned by others.</li>\n<li>We seek information, but that information is not always verified.</li>\n<li>We store our digital lives, but it's not always secure.</li>\n<li>We share with our loved ones and our networks, but what we share is sometimes tracked and not owned by us.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Our digital lives have become complicated, inefficient, and insecure. The web that was supposed to connect us has started to ensnare us.</p>\n<h2 id=\"what-should-be-done-and-how-are-we-solving-the-problem\"><a href=\"#what-should-be-done-and-how-are-we-solving-the-problem\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>What should be done and How are we solving the problem?</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Crystal Twin is a completely redesigned way to navigate your digital world with YOU at the center. </li>\n<li>Crystal Twin is your digital ally, keeping your data safe while making the Internet simple, more efficient, and sustainable for the planet.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"why-is-crystal-twin-important\"><a href=\"#why-is-crystal-twin-important\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Why is Crystal Twin important?</h2>\n<p>Have you seen The Social Dilemma? Well, we can break away. Crystal Twin creates a bright new and free digital world.</p>\n","sidebar":"docs","next":"/docs/decentralized-we-intro/","prev":"/docs/digitalme-id/","headings":[{"depth":1,"value":"Crystal Twin","anchor":"#crystal-twin"},{"depth":2,"value":"What is happening today?","anchor":"#what-is-happening-today"},{"depth":2,"value":"What should be done and How are we solving the problem?","anchor":"#what-should-be-done-and-how-are-we-solving-the-problem"},{"depth":2,"value":"Why is Crystal Twin important?","anchor":"#why-is-crystal-twin-important"}]},"allMarkdownPage":{"edges":[{"node":{"path":"/docs/zeroci/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/wiki-publisher/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/virtual-spaces/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/video-sharing/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/video-conf/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/tomochain/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/tfgrid/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/serverless/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/publishing-tool/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/index/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/harmony/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/gridsome/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/gitea/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/dmcustomers/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/dmcollab/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/dmcircles